Raspberry pi, particle argon and bbs microbit project to controll and connect to projector.


#BBC Microbit electronic blind reciever micropython
	blind_reciever.py 

#BBC Microbit electronic blind controler micropython
	blind_sender.py

#script for raspberry pi to turn on projector
	remote.py

#script for raspberry pi that will enable mqqt comunication with volume remote
	volume_control.py

#script for raspberry pi to turn off projector when Kodi close
	remote_off.py 

# Particle Argon code to send potentiometer values to raspberry pi 
	vol_controller.c

